title: BBC, PBS, Nova - Vikings, Pagans and Indians
description:
This is a compilation of 8 historical documentaries. If you like any one of these then there is a great chance that you like the others as well.
Several of the documentaries are among the absolute favourites of mine.

30 files, DivX and XviD only, English language, no subs

Enjoy!
